
## Data Model

The model of the server schema used is the following:

![Database Schema](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/118762770/349137141-1a29ef6c-fe1b-46ea-9140-701704dd6d09.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJnaXRodWIuY29tIiwiYXVkIjoicmF3LmdpdGh1YnVzZXJjb250ZW50LmNvbSIsImtleSI6ImtleTUiLCJleHAiOjE3MjExNDA3ODYsIm5iZiI6MTcyMTE0MDQ4NiwicGF0aCI6Ii8xMTg3NjI3NzAvMzQ5MTM3MTQxLTFhMjllZjZjLWZlMWItNDZlYS05MTQwLTcwMTcwNGRkNmQwOS5wbmc_.QHYWtuJKpbJRYDT_KCZj_gsDAe0GfG5jSwkq51fZRcU)

The main objects are:
- Users: which are the people that log in to the system.
- Drones: which are the drones that are registered in the system.
- Missions: which are the missions that are created in the system and performed with multiple drones.
